title: Add Customer: redirect on the page Add Customer via clicking the button Add Customer on the main page

title: Add Customer: redirect on the page Add Customer via  Hamburger menu

1. Click on the Hamburger menu
2. Choose Add Customer button

2. User is redirected on the relevant page

title: Add customer: Background Check allows to choose Done or Pending radio buttons
steps_actions:
1. Click on the radio button "Done"
2. Click on the radio button "Pending"
steps_result:
1. The radio button "Done" is selected. The radio button 
"Pending" isn't selected
2. The radio button "Pending" is selected. The radio button "Done" isn't selected

title: Add Customer: FirstName validation (empty value)
preconditions: The page https://demo.guru99.com/telecom/addcustomer.php is open. All fields except FirstName filled with valid data
steps_actions:
1. Select the FirstName field
2. Leave the field FirstName empty
3. Click Submit button
4. Close the modal message
5. Click Submit button
steps_result:
1. The FirstName is selected
2. FirstName field is empty
3. The modal window appears with a message" Please fill all fields"
4. The modal window disappeared
5. The message 'First name must not be blank' is presented under the FirstName field
